        %h1 foreach Loop
        %p  The foreach loop works only on arrays, and is used to loop through each key/value pair in an array

        :javascript
           str1 = ' <i>  red  <br> green  <br> blue   <br> yellow <br>  </i> '
            document.write(str1) 
           
        / ::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
        / ------ end text --------
