        / ::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
        &lt;h1>  foreach Loop &lt;/h1>
        &lt;p> The foreach loop works only on arrays, and is used to loop through each key/value pair in an array   &lt;/p>
        / ::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
        &lt;/body>
      / ------ end html --------
